lead_paragraph: Thousands of gun rights supporters rallied outside New York's Capitol Tuesday to call for the repeal of gun control measures championed by Gov. Andrew Cuomo, which they intend to use as a rallying cry in the fall elections.

headline.main: Trump Rallies Against Cuomo, New York Gun Control
headline.print_headline: Trump Rallies Against Cuomo, New York Gun Control
